                  </hi>. (<hi rend="italic">policeman</hi>). I apprehended the prisoner on the 29th Jan.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> With regard to the embezzlement, I have a set off due to me for commission on goods sold, and the prosecutors have a letter of guarantee for 100<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. from my father.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18570302-name-19" type="witnessName">
