                        <interp inst="t18570302-name-19" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN LYON</persName>
                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> At the time I paid his wages, he made no claim on me for commission—the amount due to him, supposing all the orders were paid, would be a fraction below 8<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I made an application to you for a sovereign commission on the night when I was supposed to be discharged. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> You did not.</p>
